{"id": 2931, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中你都有哪些意外发现自我的时刻？", "description": "一些”不经意间对自己有了更深的理解和反思”的瞬间。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jesadaphorn）", "record_count": 2278, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190506111346706CxeYSIGhOtoBZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-07T03:00:08Z", "options": [{"id": 343040, "content": "换了新的环境，意识到自己只是个世俗的普通人，接受自己的不优秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650173}, {"id": 343041, "content": "给朋友训哭的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638053}, {"id": 343047, "content": "写一篇文章，发现自己连个属于自己的想法都没有的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617514}, {"id": 343560, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 343058, "content": "一个人的时候就会想很多，会发现另一个自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418086}, {"id": 343065, "content": "觉着自己满口骚话 聊的别人神魂颠倒 最后还是才知道字迹是鱼塘里的最安分那鱼🐟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538954}, {"id": 344858, "content": "我一直以为提到曾经伤心过的事可以笑着说出来，也有很多很多次我确实把那些很难过的东西轻松坦率的表达出来。直到许多个不知名的夜深人静的晚上，发现不经意间掠过的悲伤，还是会叫自己像十二岁那年一样掉眼泪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482221}, {"id": 345628, "content": "每月15号开始对比花呗与银行短信上的阿拉伯数字谁大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656933}, {"id": 343326, "content": "照镜子的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454775}, {"id": 343074, "content": "每次照镜子的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650230}, {"id": 343589, "content": "尴尬突然沉默的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630954}, {"id": 343084, "content": "任何跟考试有关的时候，会迅速反思这些时间都在干嘛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 343341, "content": "写需求的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108007}, {"id": 343094, "content": "晚上睡觉的时候、心情低落的时候、犯错的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20190508175433IUghprMxAZLP7O6W.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607376}, {"id": 343096, "content": "控制不住情绪的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494663}, {"id": 343101, "content": "剪完头发后再看看没剪之前的照片，骂自己为什么要剪这发型。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650388}, {"id": 343111, "content": "唱歌入迷\n独自完成某件事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996152}, {"id": 343624, "content": "想起以前说的胡话\n做的尴尬事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 345164, "content": "做梦的时候,发现白天不在意的情感会在梦中的被放大,算是小小的执念吧.", "image": "img/option/option/20190524133857TRFzCPsnfvZo1Jru.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574767}, {"id": 343123, "content": "从朋友口中听到意想不到的评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387200}, {"id": 343125, "content": "暗恋女孩子的时候，充分认识到自己是个舔狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469711}, {"id": 343127, "content": "跟朋友发生冲突的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1539682}, {"id": 343143, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008121}, {"id": 346218, "content": "花呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 343659, "content": "觉得自己很胖，可是男朋友却说一点都不胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461235}, {"id": 343409, "content": "分手失恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622567}, {"id": 343695, "content": "没有自我 自我是它人的概念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652182}, {"id": 342931, "content": "换位思考的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644423}, {"id": 342932, "content": "健身两年后，以为吃顿大餐就会胖成猪，实际吃了几天身材还是在，线条很紧致", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254687}, {"id": 342933, "content": "穿上新鞋被人盯，蜜汁嘚瑟，啊，虚荣啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509686}, {"id": 343189, "content": "当下的自己看以前的日记", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140809}, {"id": 342934, "content": "跌入低谷的自我反思的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647827}, {"id": 342936, "content": "以为自己高冷孤独，直到花痴一样追过一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 150, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459603}, {"id": 342937, "content": "写简历的时候，发现自己做了很多但有用的却不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 326, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649680}, {"id": 342938, "content": "去洗手间不经意间看到自己帅气的脸庞（意淫", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320188}, {"id": 342940, "content": "自以为文笔好，然后在乐乎发表了一篇同人文，一百多热度，哦，原来自己是个渣(๑˙ー˙๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486579}, {"id": 342941, "content": "在独处的时间会，尤其上厕所的时候，我上厕所没有看手机的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435946}, {"id": 342942, "content": "看到别人的微博妙笔生花妙语连珠而我只会说“俺也一样”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 342943, "content": "每月工资扣除房租水电……不如当地实习生过得滋润。", "image": "img/option/option/20190507115959YoT3tFvD1drg2OXx.jpg", "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632590}, {"id": 342944, "content": "翻到以前写的日记/文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 342945, "content": "挑战自己极限的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649707}, {"id": 342946, "content": "有一天称重瘦了4斤，开心的下楼跑了五公里，并在朋友圈炫了一波。结果第二天称才发现称出问题了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625744}, {"id": 343202, "content": "洗澡时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628356}, {"id": 342948, "content": "想法跟以前有所改变的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461099}, {"id": 343204, "content": "遇到不靠谱的人，做不靠谱的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620235}, {"id": 342950, "content": "看几年前自己发的QQ说说的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950098}, {"id": 342951, "content": "哼着小曲儿的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 342952, "content": "临近deadline时候，发现自己可能是个潜在的“工作狂”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 342953, "content": "在逼迫自己完成超额任务并最终做到的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649266}, {"id": 342954, "content": "以为自己学习挺认真，直到看见成绩那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}]}